highlights.text: KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs Singapore. “Golden” is the highest at #14.
“Vaa Vaa Pakkam Vaa - Remix” by DJ Gowtham, Ilaiyaraaja, S. P. Balasubrahmanyam, and Vani Jairam is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Singapore at #18.
“有一种遗憾叫我们” by 田园 has been on Viral Songs Singapore the longest, at 123 days straight.
“tower of memories” by ivri is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Singapore, up 20 spots at #73.
